{"h57133275g5d2ag4d07g9ac2ged40606774a4": ["Would you look at this place? Such a pastoral escape. Free of predators. Annoyances. <i>Obligations.</i>", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_SchoolOgres_CFM_DebtCollection.html", "2bfcf6a6-9831-2159-33c3-5a475c84bbdd"], "hef726fd8g0785g42e6g9958gecff7614c653": ["One excepted, of course. We made a bargain, sweet stuff - and I've come to collect.", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_SchoolOgres_CFM_DebtCollection.html", "7f9e607d-0843-58a4-9c1a-513d80ac2048"], "h0ccfd920gb3a7g4b54g981bgeef70206dbe0": ["<i>Pay him what you promised. </i>([463b0f43-5410-412d-aba3-875cf81c38ca] gold)", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_SchoolOgres_CFM_DebtCollection.html", "b01b7f1d-e994-232c-7984-eed2b67f1141"], "h48c43c5egc4f2g4774g845fg1beb0d83c5ca": ["Consider your debt paid. I will leave your flesh unbroken.", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_SchoolOgres_CFM_DebtCollection.html", "924978a4-be5e-4216-f00f-08fba21aa5ba"], "h06f303b5g5e79g4808ga15cg6ab9386a3f59": ["Can I lick that mouth-watering meat of yours? A parting gift, as it were.", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_SchoolOgres_CFM_DebtCollection.html", "5fe5590f-dcff-1dfa-ca05-ba1bbbbd9ed8"], "h742b934cgcb90g4e40ga105g0d0703f7e5b6": ["Disgusting. I'm not letting you lick me.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_SchoolOgres_CFM_DebtCollection.html", "9d6a1d9d-423c-31ae-9223-8b92c45c39c3"], "hb9e94e16g1b71g4e65g8585g86061ea1be0c": ["A pity for us both.", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_SchoolOgres_CFM_DebtCollection.html", "cb828fb4-eacd-b64e-36bb-5a9785de8d5a"], "hb2392ed1gc327g42a6g9ac7gf05da6ccc5a8": ["<i>Offer your arm. </i>One lick.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_SchoolOgres_CFM_DebtCollection.html", "43ee76ce-02ce-fc85-6df0-ee7ba3b98853"], "h8e1d6b4eg4c6eg4193ga650ga4847c1f5dd8": ["Consider me satisfied.", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_SchoolOgres_CFM_DebtCollection.html", "eea3c3dc-2306-1107-6359-61e5c544d91c"], "hacd6f448g4b6cg491agac3ag585571a2255a": ["<i>Pay him what you promised. </i>([01f129ea-b4dc-44b6-8154-9a948f876a82] gold)", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_SchoolOgres_CFM_DebtCollection.html", "f7d1f335-4dcd-6507-3023-aa53d5504e5e"], "h824a2b5egc46cg4bd4gbd52g702b80772f7c": ["<i>Pay him what you promised. </i>([5dac5eea-faeb-459c-b675-46c51519b784] gold)", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_SchoolOgres_CFM_DebtCollection.html", "5798fa3b-3594-0e44-ec05-02befa61bcb0"], "hdd434b3agfae9g4cb6g8b73g2b66bad7849c": ["We have a new bargain: I pay nothing, and you leave the camp alive.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_SchoolOgres_CFM_DebtCollection.html", "78bec906-74be-3f56-dc0c-74bcbe92aef1"], "h223bc3d1g7eccg4b79g81c6g9bb48adc5eea": ["Mmm. That's a fight I may not win. Pity, too - I found an ale that would pair nicely with your marrow.", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_SchoolOgres_CFM_DebtCollection.html", "c2e36f53-d065-0625-8ce4-8dcba9d42d89"], "h29fef136g022cg453dgaf03gfe71831ea4e3": ["Alas, I must find another's bones to crack.", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_SchoolOgres_CFM_DebtCollection.html", "61bb95e9-6cca-1ecc-f24e-60cfe58897b6"], "ha2ef9bf5gb740g4aa8g8974g6d37afb68f92": ["No deal. But I'll pay you twice what I owe you - next time.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_SchoolOgres_CFM_DebtCollection.html", "b20a4c5e-a2f9-9a2b-f9fd-8afdafff10c1"], "h313eb746g1ddbg4b2eg9666g015195802184": ["You think my mind so flaccid? I will crack your bones and suck their marrow!", "848b6f10-3ae5-41f6-b1a1-98c34a19ba3f", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_SchoolOgres_CFM_DebtCollection.html", "e00411fd-1f7e-da20-e581-7f977cd5c747"], "h9c471933g0662g4a38gb43eg7cff1aa0ff25": ["<i>Move in for the kill.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_SchoolOgres_CFM_DebtCollection.html", "0fe8c73a-305f-b965-424d-3f95a35bdf14"]}